Description: Why have others chosen the insurance profession? Let’s hear from your fellow Agents to find out their story. Are your motivations similar to theirs?

Name: [PAMB EN] Learn from Your Fellow Agents: Managing Customer Risks with SAP
Description: Understanding and mastering the steps of the Sales Advisory Process can help you to better manage your customers’ risks. Learn from your fellow Agents on how they do so by watching the following videos.

Name: [PAMB EN] Learn from Your Fellow Agents: Maximising Productivity to Achieve Success
Description: There are only so many hours in a day, so making the most of your time is critical. Watch the following videos to learn about the tactics your fellow Agents have mastered to maximise their productivity and achieve success.

Name: [PAMB EN] Learn From Your Fellow Agents: Sourcing Prospects
Description: Sourcing prospects is the heart of building pipelines. As an important tool in an excellent Agent’s toolkit, it is vital to know the best ways to source prospects. Let’s see how other Agents have done this—with success.

Name: [PAMB EN] Learn from Your Fellow Agents: Understanding the SAP and the Four Arts
